                "text": "Vulnerability CVE-2024-11053\nSeverity: low\nPackage: curl\nVersion: 7.76.1-35.el9_7.3\nFix Version: \nType: rpm\nLocation: /var/lib/rpm/rpmdb.sqlite\nData Namespace: redhat:distro:redhat:9\nLink: [CVE-2024-11053](https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/CVE-2024-11053)",
