              "id": "CVE-2024-9681-curl",
              "name": "RpmMatcherExactDirectMatch",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2024-9681 low vulnerability for curl package"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "A vulnerability was found in curl. When curl is asked to use HSTS, the expiry time for a subdomain might overwrite a parent domain's cache entry, making it end sooner or later than intended."
